Fish and Boat is a recreational newspaper for fishing and boating based in North Queensland, Australia. The paper is published montly and most of the stories are contributed by readers themselves. The paper has been running for 25 years.
The current editor of the paper is Anthony Gomes, after Harold Bligh retired and the paper has now had three ownerships.
 
